{"tid":1625750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"睇撚透班藍絲","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:33:24.000Z","uid":247790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a22eaffb931e51d874cccf56fce27bdaa62aa9","tid":1625750,"uid":247790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲係藍絲嘅智商基本上係負值<br />\n大家唔洗白費心機去勸佢地<br />\n就算宵禁佢地都會話係示威者造成<br />\n搭車見到有藍絲喺到屌話暴徒點點點<br />\n唔撚洗同佢講道理<br />\n屌都廢鳩事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過如果佢地出手打人<br />\n一定要獅鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fc3151e1caea5310f7a2f97e49cba70942dbc28a","tid":1625750,"uid":247790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"61c0b3f713f34e9b3c887756af5e5a279a4ad51c","tid":1625750,"uid":247790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2301797ec8aaa838e2c2b2edc7b238298ea38694","tid":1625750,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61c0b3f713f34e9b3c887756af5e5a279a4ad51c","tid":1625750,"uid":247790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"}]}